      KVM: PPC: Book3S: Add ONE_REG register names that were missed
      KVM: PPC: Add CAP to indicate hcall fixes
      KVM: PPC: MPIC: Reset IRQ source private members
      KVM: PPC: Graciously fail broken LE hypercalls
